      <div class="logo">CG</div>
      <div>
        <h1>ChatGPT WebApp — Install & Configuration</h1>
        <p class="lead">Install & edit instructions. English + Português — short, copyable and pretty.</p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <section class="grid">
      <article class="card">
        <h2>EN — Quick, clean instructions</h2>
        <p class="muted">Installer copies files and handles dependencies. Run the installer then edit the rules and shortcut.</p>

        <div style="margin-top:8px">
          <strong>1) Install</strong>
          <div class="code-wrap" style="margin-top:8px">
            <button class="copy" data-target="#install-en">Copy</button>
            <pre id="install-en"><code>chmod +x install.sh
./install.sh</code></pre>
          </div>

          <p class="muted" style="margin-top:10px">Installed paths used below:</p>
          <div class="paths">~/.local/share/applications/WebApp-ChatGPT4319.desktop<br>~/.config/devilspie2/chatgpt.sh<br>~/.config/devilspie2/chatgpt.lua</div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:14px">
          <strong>2) Edit <code>chatgpt.lua</code></strong>
          <p class="muted">File: <code>~/.config/devilspie2/chatgpt.lua</code></p>
          <div class="code-wrap" style="margin-top:8px">
            <button class="copy" data-target="#lua-ex">Copy</button>
            <pre id="lua-ex"><code>if get_window_class() == "WebApp-ChatGPT4319" then
    set_window_geometry(1320, 680, 600, 400) -- X, Y, width, height
    make_always_on_top()
end</code></pre>
          </div>

          <p class="muted" style="margin-top:8px">What to change (short):</p>
          <ul style="margin:6px 0 0 18px;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px">
            <li><code>get_window_class()</code> — keep <code>"WebApp-ChatGPT4319"</code> unless you changed the .desktop class.</li>
            <li><code>set_window_geometry(X, Y, W, H)</code> — X horizontal, Y vertical, W width, H height.</li>
            <li><code>make_always_on_top()</code> — comment to disable: <code>-- make_always_on_top()</code>.</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="code-wrap" style="margin-top:8px">
            <button class="copy" data-target="#reload-en">Copy</button>
            <pre id="reload-en"><code>pkill devilspie2
devilspie2 &</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:12px">
          <strong>3) Configure keyboard shortcut (manual)</strong>
          <p class="muted">Command to assign:</p>
          <div class="code-wrap" style="margin-top:8px">
            <button class="copy" data-target="#shortcut-en">Copy</button>
            <pre id="shortcut-en"><code>bash ~/.config/devilspie2/chatgpt.sh</code></pre>
          </div>

          <p class="muted" style="margin-top:8px">Cinnamon (GUI): Settings → Keyboard → Shortcuts → Custom Shortcuts → Add new → Name: <code>ChatGPT</code>, Command: above, set key.</p>
        </div>

      </article>

      <article class="card">
        <h2>BR — Instalação e configuração</h2>
        <p class="muted">Curto, direto — o instalador já copia e instala dependências.</p>

        <div style="margin-top:8px">
          <strong>1) Instalar</strong>
          <div class="code-wrap" style="margin-top:8px">
            <button class="copy" data-target="#install-br">Copy</button>
            <pre id="install-br"><code>chmod +x install.sh
./install.sh</code></pre>
          </div>

          <p class="muted" style="margin-top:10px">Caminhos usados:</p>
          <div class="paths">~/.local/share/applications/WebApp-ChatGPT4319.desktop<br>~/.config/devilspie2/chatgpt.sh<br>~/.config/devilspie2/chatgpt.lua</div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:14px">
          <strong>2) Editar <code>chatgpt.lua</code></strong>
          <p class="muted">Arquivo: <code>~/.config/devilspie2/chatgpt.lua</code></p>
          <div class="code-wrap" style="margin-top:8px">
            <button class="copy" data-target="#lua-br">Copy</button>
            <pre id="lua-br"><code>if get_window_class() == "WebApp-ChatGPT4319" then
    set_window_geometry(1320, 680, 600, 400) -- X, Y, largura, altura
    make_always_on_top()
end</code></pre>
          </div>

          <p class="muted" style="margin-top:8px">O que alterar (resumido):</p>
          <ul style="margin:6px 0 0 18px;color:var(--muted);font-size:13px">
            <li><code>get_window_class()</code> — deixe <code>"WebApp-ChatGPT4319"</code> salvo que altere o .desktop.</li>
            <li><code>set_window_geometry(X, Y, L, A)</code> — X horizontal, Y vertical, L largura, A altura.</li>
            <li>Comente <code>make_always_on_top()</code> para desativar.</li>
          </ul>

          <div class="code-wrap" style="margin-top:8px">
            <button class="copy" data-target="#reload-br">Copy</button>
            <pre id="reload-br"><code>pkill devilspie2
devilspie2 &</code></pre>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div style="margin-top:12px">
          <strong>3) Atalho de teclado</strong>
          <div class="code-wrap" style="margin-top:8px">
            <button class="copy" data-target="#shortcut-br">Copy</button>
            <pre id="shortcut-br"><code>bash ~/.config/devilspie2/chatgpt.sh</code></pre>
          </div>

          <p class="muted" style="margin-top:8px">Cinnamon: Configurações → Teclado → Atalhos → Atalhos personalizados → Adicionar → Nome: <code>ChatGPT</code>, Comando: acima, defina a tecla.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </section>

    <div class="card" style="margin-top:18px">
      <h2>Notes & tips</h2>
      <p class="note">Keep the <code>.desktop</code> Class consistent with <code>get_window_class()</code>. If you changed the Desktop file, update the class string in the <code>chatgpt.lua</code> rule.</p>
      <p class="note">Reload rules after editing: <code>pkill devilspie2 && devilspie2 &</code></p>
    </div>

    <footer>Copy buttons work per block. Open this file in a browser to use the copy feature.</footer>
  </main>

  <script>
    document.querySelectorAll('.copy').forEach(btn => {
      btn.addEventListener('click', ()=>{
        const target = document.querySelector(btn.dataset.target);
        if(!target) return;
        navigator.clipboard.writeText(target.innerText).then(()=>{
          btn.textContent = 'Copied';
          setTimeout(()=> btn.textContent = 'Copy',900);
        }).catch(()=>{
          btn.textContent = 'Error';
          setTimeout(()=> btn.textContent = 'Copy',900);
        })   
      })
    })
  </script>
